    "description": {
      "value": "<p>@Compendium[compendiums-mix-dnd5e.um5-rules.R1ew21i3luHJHfV5]{UM5 Ch.6: Gear}</p>\n<p><span class=\"fontstyle0\">They say clothing makes a man. In this case, they can also help you with skill checks. In an appropriate situation (GM's call) you gain the listed bonus to skill checks. With the exception of wearing synthetic weave, you gain no benefits from these clothes if trying to wear them underneath or (if possible) over your armor or other clothes. Casual wear grants no benefit.</span></p>\n<p><strong><span class=\"fontstyle0\">Formal</span></strong><span class=\"fontstyle0\" style=\"font-size: 11pt;\">: </span><span class=\"fontstyle0\">Gain a +2 bonus to Charisma (Persuasion) checks</span> <br style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: normal; text-align: -webkit-auto; text-size-adjust: auto;\"><br></p>",
